__section__
default
__description__
Print a label next to a form element

* value = label
* comment = comment to put next to label
* nobreak = no BR at end or P at beginning

__title__

__page__
misc
__lang__
en_US
__name__
formLabel
__template__
[% UNLESS nobreak %]<p>[% END %]<font color="[% user.colors.bg_3 %]"><b>[% value | strip_html %]</b></font>
[% IF comment %]([% comment | strip_html %])[% END %][% UNLESS nobreak %]<br>[% END %]

__seclev__
10000
__version__
$Id: formLabel;misc;default,v 1.7 2004/09/24 23:44:11 pudge Exp $
